# 🚀 AI Roadmap Generator (Groq Integration)

## 📌 Overview

This project uses **Groq API** to generate personalized learning roadmaps based on user input such as role, tech stack, and goals.

Instead of relying on unstable AI SDKs, we use a **direct REST API approach** for reliability and speed.

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

* Node.js (Backend)
* Express.js
* Axios (HTTP client)
* Groq API (LLM)

---

