## 🎯 API Endpoint

### Generate Roadmap

```http
POST /api/roadmap/generate
```

### Request Body

```json
{
  "role": "Backend Developer",
  "techStack": ["Node.js", "MongoDB"],
  "level": "beginner",
  "timeCommitment": "2 hours/day",
  "deadline": "3 months",
  "goalType": "job",
  "projects": "yes"
}
```

---

### Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": "Week 1: Learn Node.js...\nWeek 2: ..."
}
```

